[{"Id": 1014930, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Mu’awiyah ibn Ammar has reported the following: I once asked Imam Sadiq (a) to teach me a supplicatory prayer for more sustenance. He therefore taught me a supplicatory prayer that I have never seen more effective than it. It is the following…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Muawiya bin Ammar se manqool hai keh mai ne Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) se arz kiya keh mujhe wus’at-e-rizq ki (ziyaadah rizq ke liye) koi dua farmaaye, to Aap (a) ne mujh ko yeh dua taaleem farmaayi aur mai ne wus’at-e-rizq ke liye is se behtar kisi cheez ko nahi paaya…", "UrduDescription": "معاویہ ابن عمار سے منقول ہے کہ میں نے امام جعفر صادق ؑ سے عرض کیا : مجھے وسعت رزق کی کوئی دعا تعلیم فرمائیں تو آپ ؑ نے مجھ کو یہ دعا تعلیم فرمائی اور میں نے وسعتِ رزق کے لئے اس سے بہتر کسی چیز کو نہیں پایا۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, 