icBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014931, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, (please) provide me out of Your all-inclusive, legal, and pleasant sustenance with sustenance that is expansive, legally gotten, pleasant, covering all this-worldly and other-worldly demands, pouring, torrential, enjoyable, and wholesome, without exhaustive affairs and without the favor of any of Your creatures; rather, with a favor out of Your all-inclusive favors. You have said, “Ask Allah of His grace.” Thus, from Your grace only do I ask, from Your gift only do I ask, and from Your abounding donation do I ask.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mujhe ataa farma apne be-hisaab fazl se halaal o paakeeza faraawa’n rozi jo halaal o paakeeza aur kaafi ho duniya o aakherat ke liye, woh jaari rahe munaasib aur khoosh zaaeqa bagair kisi takleef ke aur us mein Teri makhluq mein se kisi ka ehsaan na ho magar yeh keh Tere wasee fazl se farawaani miley kyu-keh Tu ne farmaaya hai keh: “Allah ke fazl se maango’n” pas mai Tere fazl se maangta hu Teri ataa mai talab karta hu aur Tere bhare haatho’n se lena chahta hu.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! مجھے عطا فرما اپنے بے حساب فضل سے حلا ل و پاکیزہ فراوان روزی جو حلال و پاکیزہ اور کافی ہو دنیا و آخرت کے لئے وہ جاری رہے مناسب اور خوش ذائقہ بغیر کسی تکلیف کے اور اس میں تیری مخلوق میں سے کسی کا احسان نہ ہو مگر یہ کہ تیرے وسیع فضل سے فراوانی ملے کیو ں کہ تو نے فرمایا ہے کہ اللہ کے فضل سے مانگو پس میں تیرے فضل سے مانگتا ہوں تیری عطا میں طلب کرتا ہوں اور تیرے بھرے ہاتھ سے لینا چاہتا ہوں۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUM-MAR ZUKNEE MIN FAZLE-KAL WAASE-I’L HALAA-LIT TAIYYE-BE RIZQAN WAASE-AN HALAA-LAN TAIYYE-BAN BALAA-GHAN LID-DUNYAA WAL AAKHE-RATE SABBAN SABBAN HANIYYA-AN MIN GHAIRE KADDIN WA LAA MANNIN MIN AHA-DIM MIN KHALQE-KA ILLAA SA-A’TAN MIN FAZLE-KAL WAASE-E’ FA-INNA-KA QULTA WAS-A-LUL LAAHA MIN FAZLE-HI FA-MIN FAZLE-KA AS-ALO WA MIN A’TIYYA-TEKA AS-ALO WA MIN YADE-KAL MAL AS-ALO.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ ارْزُقْنِىْ مِنْ فَضْلِكَ الْوَاسِعِ الْحَلَالِ الطَّيِّبِ رِزْقًا وَاسِعًا حَلَالًا طَيِّبًا بَلَاغًا لِلدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ صَبًّا صَبًّا هَنيَّئًا مَرِيْئًا مِنْ غَيْرِ كَدٍّ وَلَا مَنٍّ مِنْ اَحَدٍ مِّنْ خَلْقِكَ اِلَّا سَعَةً مِنْ فَضْلِكَ الْوَاسِعِ فَاِنَّكَ قُلْتَ وَاسْئَلُوا اللهَ مِنْ فَضْلِهٖ فَمِنْ فَضْلِكَ اَسْئَلُ وَمِنْ عَطِيَّتِكَ اَسْئَلُ وَمِنْ يَدِكَ الْمَلْا اَسْئَلُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign1